    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Zest the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
