    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> cooked meat-free chicken </strong>to the<strong> softened leek</strong> along with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 6,
